.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, kale, peas
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, basketball, lacrosse, golf
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the owner of the dog and the person who's sport is basketball##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8
 6. the person eating peas is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is the owner of the frog##1
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##8
18. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| Food          | peas     | grapes | carrot | kale  |
| Sport   | basketball    | lacrosse  | golf | sailing |
| Pet           | goldfish | rabbit | dog    | frog  |

