The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
House: wooden, craftsman, tower, modern
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, snowmobile
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the modern house##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the craftsman house##8
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the tower house##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee   | water     | mirinda    | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul      | reggae     | folk     |
| House         | wooden | tower  | modern     | craftsman  |
| Transport     | bike     | quad-bike | snowmobile | boat     |

